Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.03,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:14.16,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Já tě mám, Taito,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:16.70,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ráda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.62,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím to dát do pořádku, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.96,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I když tím zraním Haruku....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:28.04,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Slíbil jsem Himee, že budu vždycky s ní.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:31.67,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\frx10\fry8\frz301\fnCooper Black\b0\pos(478,291)}Dům Shigure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.67,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.97,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, haló haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.43,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Co je, Haruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.43,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taito?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.14,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.68,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Teta Shigure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.56,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Taito....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.52,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka je s tebou, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.69,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ne, není.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:51.23,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nelži mi, ano?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.57,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli je, nebudu se zlobit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.45,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudu se zlobit, ať už děláte cokoliv.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.74,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poč- Co to říkáš, Teti?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:00.74,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vůbec nechápu, co se děje.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.62,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka se nevrátila domů.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.21,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Už je tak pozdě,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.67,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ale nezvedá mi telefon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.76,Itsuka Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy jste...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:43.16,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}dakara ikanaide boku no inai mirai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:43.16,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Nekráčej vstříc budoucnosti beze mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:50.38,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}ano isshun no omoi wo mada wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:50.38,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Nedokážu zapomenou na tvou nečekanou náklonost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:55.97,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}ano hi mune ni oku migi shimeta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:55.97,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Tvé slova si, od toho dne, držím ve svém srdci.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.88,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}ano hitokoto ga ashita wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.88,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}S těmi slovy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.05,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}tsukuwaretan dane {SOMEONE FIX THIS IT'S WRONG}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.05,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}jsi mě zachránil.
