Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:05.06,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}To musel být sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.52,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}sore wa boku no te no yume no kana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.52,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Ale byl ten sen můj?
