Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:27.29,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}pak bych zvládnula tyhle noci plné žalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.91,itsuka op romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}ichido dake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.91,itsuka op english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Alespoň jednou...
